<li id="cite_note-128"><b><a href="#cite_ref-128" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.scienceandsociety.co.uk/results.asp?image=10438336&amp;wwwflag=2&amp;imagepos=12" class="external free" title="http://www.scienceandsociety.co.uk/results.asp?image=10438336&amp;wwwflag=2&amp;imagepos=12" rel="nofollow">http://www.scienceandsociety.co.uk/results.asp?image=10438336&amp;wwwflag=2&amp;imagepos=12</a> &lt;Pirata, Bruja y asesina. ¡Culpable!&gt;</li>
