<li>Hobson, Chris and Noble, Andrew. <i>Falklands Air War</i>.</li>
<li>Kon, Daniel. <i>Los Chicos de la Guerra, The Argentine conscripts' own moving accounts of their Falklands War</i> (English translation). New English Library 1983. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0450056112" class="internal">ISBN 0-450-05611-2</a>.</li>
<li>McManners, Hugh, <i><a href="/wiki/Forgotten_Voices_of_the_Falklands" title="Forgotten Voices of the Falklands">Forgotten Voices of the Falklands</a></i>, <a href="/wiki/Ebury_Press" title="Ebury Press" class="mw-redirect">Ebury Press</a>, 2007, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780091908805" class="internal">ISBN 9780091908805</a></li>
