<li>Middlebrook, Martin. <i>The Argentine Fight for the Falklands</i>. Pen &amp; Sword Military Classics, 2003. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0850529786" class="internal">ISBN 0-85052-978-6</a></li>
<li>Norton-Taylor, Richard. <i>The Ponting Affair</i>. Cecil Woolf, 1985. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0900821736" class="internal">ISBN 0-900821-73-6</a>.</li>
<li>Ponting, Clive. <i>The Right to Know: The Inside Story of the Belgrano Affair</i>. Sphere Books, 1985. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0722169442" class="internal">ISBN 0-7221-6944-2</a></li>
