<li>Tinker, Lieut. David, R.N. <i>A Message from the Falklands, The Life and Gallant Death of David Tinker, Lieut. R.N. from his Letters and Poems</i>. Penguin, 1982. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0140067787" class="internal">ISBN 0-14-006778-7</a>.</li>
<li>Thornton, Richard C. 'The Falklands Sting<i>. Brassey's, 1998. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1574881558" class="internal">ISBN 1-57488-155-8</a>.</i></li>
